G5. Please select Village name or Urban Area (in %area_council%)

G2b. What is the PRIMARY phone number used to contact this school or health?
qstn.ivuInstr: NOTE: This phone number will be used if the household or institution needs to be contacted for any reason after enumeration is complete. For example validation checks by the Supervisor. Please comment if the number is from a landline.

qstn.qstnLit: G4. Please record the location of this household or institution. FOLLOW THE RULES BELOW:
qstn.ivuInstr: 1. GPS can not be taken inside a building. 2. When you turn the GPS/location mode on wait at least 1 minute before trying to take a location. You will get a validation error if the accuracy is not better than 20m. Stand on the same spot and press the GPS button again. 3. Stand at least 10m away from the wall of a building 4. Make sure you can see the sky 5. Don't stand under a tree unless there is no other option
